description: A line-based icon pack with a Material You color palette. Arcticons Material You is a line-based icon pack that adapts to your background! Featuring over 12.000 elegant and consistent icons, created by a community from all around the world. Arcticons Material You is a variation of the more traditional Arcticons Dark & Light icons, but with a big difference: A line color and background that change based on your wallpaper and system theme!¬† You can request new icons if you're missing any with the in-app icon request option. But it's also possible to create them yourself. If you're missing icons, you can submit an icon request or create them yourself!
